  "description": [
    "ELEVEN FRENCH FASCISM AIOED BY TRUST HITS DEMOCRACY Special to The Leader LONDON The Paris correspon dent of The Daily Herald reports that French Fascism supported by the Comite des Forges the I tench steel trust is rooking progress against democracy This Fascism has an international and a national program which is a menace to peace and progress It demands that France hold on to the left bank of the Rhine and to the Ruhr and it prepares to suppress with an iron hell all movements of French labor to improve its stan dard of living A friend of President Millerand and a prominent member of the Coroite des Forges Mr Laurent who used to be French ambassador in Berlin is quoted to the effect that France cannot overcome its financial and eco nomic crisis without first suppressing constitutional rights and establish ing a dictatorship after the model of Mussolini Paves Way for Dictator Deputy Paul Reynaud an agent of the Comite des Forges has odered a bill in the chamber of deputies which seeks to establish a dictatorship by banks and corporations Efforts are being made by the re actionaries to stampede the small business people into a blind"
